snippet.title: Seashine iOS App Preview
snippet.description:
Play as a fragile creature struggling to survive the silent and deadly world of the abyss.

Download on iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/seashine/id897544254?l=fr&ls=1&mt=8
Download on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=fr.pated.seashine
Download on the Amazon App Store: http://www.amazon.com/Pated-Seashine/dp/B012HF2RW4/

http://seashinegame.com
